ce:section.ce:para:
To optimize the weight of the entire system, the PCM sheath thickness was varied between 1 mm to 3 mm for both cylindrical and oval designs. The initial airspeed (
V i
) was established at 5 m/s, potentially increasing to over 60 m/s if coupled with a blade-less fan in the future [25]. The operational temperature range for a single 18,650 lithium-ion battery typically spans from 45 °C to 55 °C. To ensure safety, the minimum value within the specified range, 45 °C, was determined to be the upper-temperature limit permissible for the battery thermal management system. Thermal properties and operation parameters are summarized in Table 1 .
